# related_resources:
#   - https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/module/az.keyvault/update-azkeyvaultkey?view=azps-5.8.0#example-1--modify-a-key-to-enable-it--and-set-the-expiration-date-and-tags
# custom:
